snippet.title: First Bite - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for First Bite, a vampiric visual novel. 

One night. Three vampires. Make a deal with death, or die trying. An 18+ LGBTQ+ dark comedy visual novel that gives you a chance at a second life, after death.
